data.description:
Gated Beachside Community with 320' of Sugar White Sand, Private Deeded Bch. Home in sought after Paradise Retreat, a well planned high elevation Community with Rare No. & So. Entrance Gates. This well maintained, 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath Brick home with gas heated pool & Unique Florida Room, features; Gas Tankless Water Heater, 2 Car Garage/4 Car Driveway parking, tile flooring throughout. The Kitchen with breakfast Bar feature Granite Countertops & tile backsplash as do both baths. Primary Tub/Shower combo is tiled. Appliances; Refrig., DW, Washer/Dry are newly replaced. Garage Floor Epoxy Painted. Perfectly landscaped yard can be a Primary, 2nd Home or Vacation Rental. Rental Ready. Owner primary use is as 2nd home during peak STR season, Memorial Day to September 1st. Owner has some off season STR history of $50K to $65K. 2023 New Roof, HVAC, Refrig.,DW; 2022 Washer & Dryer; 2018 Gas Tankless Hot Water Heater & Gas Pool Heater, see documents.  
Scenic Gulf Drive has Bike/Pedestrian Paths and beach boardwalk along Scenic Gulf Dr. offering breathtaking Beach & Gulf Views. This Community is in a great location as is this home at an est. 400 yards from the beach. Also located close to one of South Walton's largest Public Beaches with Manmade, Dolphin Reef for snorkeling, parking areas & public bathrooms are near famous Pompano Joe's Beachside restaurant offering Caribbean style seafood & tropical cocktails for beach front takeout ordering or dining in. Just 1 block to the west is Captain Dave's on the Gulf, the oldest Destin Restaurants and Kenny D's Cajun bar & eatery.
